Package: tidySpectR
Title: Tidy Chemometrics
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Gregoire",
           family = "Denay",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "gregoire.denay@cvua-rrw.de")
Description: The aim of this package is to provide tidy methods for the 
    analysis of spectral dataset in order to improve 
    accessibility and reproducibility of chemometric analysis.
